============================================================
PHASE 6 OBJECTIVE
============================================================

Build the complete content automation pipeline for zDash.

Main goals:

1. Create Editor Agent
2. Create Graphic Agent
3. Create Social Agent
4. Build content pipeline orchestration:
   Editor → Graphic → Social
5. Add AI image generation adapter interface
6. Add mock image generation adapter
7. Add social media adapter interface
8. Add mock social media adapter
9. Add approval-required publishing workflow
10. Add scheduled content workflow
11. Add content item store
12. Add content logs and audit trail
13. Add FastAPI content endpoints
14. Integrate Phase 4 scheduler content_pipeline job with real Phase 6 service
15. Add tests for the entire content system

IMPORTANT:
- Auto-posting must be disabled by default.
- SOCIAL_DRY_RUN must be true by default.
- SOCIAL_APPROVAL_REQUIRED must be true by default.
- No social post may be published unless approval is granted.
- Do not hardcode social API tokens.
- Do not generate deceptive, spammy, misleading, impersonation, or policy-violating content.
- All external integrations must be replaceable through adapter interfaces.
- Use mock adapters when real APIs are unavailable.
- All content actions must be logged.

